<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="latter-n">latter <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lætə(r)/    美 /'lætər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-the">1.★ <strong>[与the连用] 后者：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Of the two choices, I prefer the latter. 
在这两种选择中，我更愿选后者。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="the-former-the-latter">the former ... the latter</h3>
<p>1.<strong>前者…后者：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>John and James are brothers. The former is a teacher; the latter is an engineer. 
约翰和詹姆斯是兄弟，前者是老师，后者是工程师。</p></div></div>